Changes:

1. Several methods were moved from TeamController to Team.
2. Unused methods in TeamController were deleted (Included "And" method).
3. ParticipantChoicesController and ParticipantChoices were deleted.
4. Functional tests were added for TeamController (there were none before).
5. Team Size input field was added to Team new view.
5. randomize_all_by_parent was fixed to create random teams based on input (was very broken before).